==English==
===Etymology===
From ''un-'' + ''lade''

===Transitive verb===
'''unlade'''
#[[unload]] something
#[[disburden]] something; take the [[burden]] from something; relieve something
#[[discharge]] the cargo from a ship

===Intransitive verb===
'''unlade'''
#discharge a cargo; discharge a burden

===Derived terms===
*[[unladen]] ''past participle''

